        "id": 2908171,
        "name": "Trevor Looney",
        "username": "Trevor_Looney",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/t/e5b9ba/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2020-06-07T23:19:56.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/note.asp?iWine=3552770&amp;iNote=8437394\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>2018 Morgen Long Chardonnay Marine</strong></a> <em>- USA, Oregon, Willamette Valley (6/7/2020)</em><br>\nThis was personally delivered to my front door by Seth himself. Amazing service! Very intense nose of green apple with a lot of spice as well. Pretty rich in the mouth with flavors of wet rock, lemon, and a faint orange element as well. A nice long and lingering finish. This is a great value!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/3X/1/4/14e5cae5591cec781a485f3c33968e8295f247bd.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-base62-sha1=\"2YRSpT6ZmdERCJPymYGefOIEWZf\" role=\"presentation\" width=\"620\" height=\"492\"></p>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>\n<p>Note: It turns out Seth and I went to high school together, a fact we learned after I signed up for his mailing list and he reached out to me. It was very cool to have him personally deliver a six pack to me earlier today and we had the chance to catch up. He\u2019s doing really great things with Chardonnay here in Oregon and I\u2019m happy to be a supporter.</p>",
